         Dear Evening MBA Student,
  The Fisher Center for Information Technology and Marketplace
Transformation (CITM) is offering the next Enabling eBusiness (EEB)
program, a workshop on November 7, 2001. The theme of this half-day workshop
is "eBusiness Transformation in Banking."  We can accommodate a limited
number of Evening MBA students at a special rate of $50  subject to space
availability. If you  would like  to  attend the event please e-mail your
request to citm@haas.berkeley.edu  preferably by noon tomorrow.  Include the
following information:

  Name:
  Company:
  Your Job Title:
  Contact (if different than the e-mail address of your message):
  eBusiness/Technology related background (1 paragraph):

  Program attached below.
   -- Arie


